                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1223" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM LANE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I have a certificate of Pitman's former conviction from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read—</hi>) I was at the trial—he is the man.</p>
